game.name: Summer Fashion Couples
game.description:
Wow! Two cute princesses Anna and Ladybug look very excited today since they want to have a date with their handsome boyfriends. They are ready to put their best to make them look awesome in front of their love. So they have hired you as their personal fashion advisor in this brand new girls game. Join Summer Fashion Couples and be prepared to pick up the best summer outfits for these beauties! We are sure that you would have a great time ahead with them. 
First, you have to help Ladybug to find out a cool and new summer outfit. Go through a wider collection of summer dresses and try to mix and match as many options as you can until you finalize the awesome result in this HTML5 dressing game! Dress her up with a fun pink color outfit combined with polka dots and a cool denim jacket with short sleeves! Combine this outfit with a pink backpack, high heels or match it with a blue blouse! You can also choose a white shirt and pair it with a denim mini skirt for her. 
Do not waste your time anymore! Your another favorite princess Anna is also waiting for her turn. Select an orange blazer with blue color vertical stripes and pair it with lovely denim shorts and fine printed leggings! You can also opt for a purple outfit over a short sleeved shirt and combine it with the matching beaded bracelets. Good luck to guide both the princesses to look beautiful on their first date! Check out more dress up games and have a blast with your friends no download required!
